text: Edmund Seger (16 February 1937 - 26 May 2019) was a German wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:2019 deaths Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Freiburg im Breisgau
